<tr ><td colspan="3" align="left" valign="top" style="padding-left:35px; padding-right:35px; padding-bottom:25px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="text2" ><h2 style="text-align: left;">Honeywell&nbsp;SmartRunway<sup>TM</sup> And SmartLanding<sup>TM</sup> Dealer STC Incentive Announcement For EGPWS -236-236 SmartRunway &amp; SmartLanding Software &nbsp;</h2>
<h2 style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="color: #191a00; font-size: 12px; line-height: 14.3999996185303px;">Below you will find the link for Honeywell's Sales Bulletin 2015-24:</span></h2>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/2015-24_SR_and_SL_Dealer_Incentives_for_Developing_and_Modifying_STCs_%28-236-236%29.pdf">2015-24 SR and SL Dealer Incentives for Developing and Modifying STCs (-236-236)</a></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span>This Honeywell Sales Bulletin supplements information provided in HSB 2015-01 (SmartRunway, SmartLanding and the original RAAS) by providing information on additional Dealer incentives for developing new Dealer owned SmartRunway and SmartLanding (&ldquo;SR/SL&rdquo;) STCs or upgrading current Dealer owned SmartRunway and SmartLanding STCs that are -228-228 or earlier software versions.</span></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;">Dealers can find 2015 sales bulletins in the new Honeywell Aerospace Website&nbsp;or in <a href="https://commerce.honeywell.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/HonSalesBulletinView?storeId=10651" target="_blank">MyAerospace</a> under sales bulletins.</p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;">Dealers must log in to view this bulletin.</p></div>
